cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper deals with rating prediction using textual contents and click data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also uses matrix factorization, which is a common technique in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and text analysis, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with social network analysis, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper deals with data mining and analytics, which falls under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
